name: Tull_Toma
content:
Tull Toma was a male Gungan who lived during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Dialogue pertaining to Tull Toma appeared in the directory tree files for the 2003 massively multiplayer online roleplaying game Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided. However, he never actually appeared on the video game's live servers as a proper non-player character.
